		}
		{
			dependencies: ["100000000000007A"]
			description: [
				"Giving your Cobblemon a berry to hold lets it activate that berry automatically during battle — no input required. When the trigger condition hits, the berry fires."
				""
				"Most berries trigger at low HP (below 50% or 25%), restoring health or curing a status condition right when you need it most. Pinch berries activate below 25% and provide stat boosts — high risk, high reward."
				""
				"Getting a berry to trigger in battle means you've built your first real held-item strategy. It won't be your last."
				""
				"&7Tip: Pinch berries activate below 25% HP — pair with a tanky Cobblemon for max effect.&r"
			]
			id: "100000000000007E"
			min_width: 340
			rewards: [
