		{
			dependencies: ["100000000000007E"]
			description: [
				"&eCobblemon Farmers&r adds structured berry farming with special layouts and mechanics that improve your yields. A full row of 8 berry plants, harvested in a single session, is a proper harvest."
				""
				"Check the Cobblemon Farmers documentation for optimal farm designs — some layouts significantly increase berry output over basic planting."
				""
				"A well-maintained berry farm means you'll never run dry on healing items or battle consumables, no matter how deep into the harder chapters you go."
				""
				"&7Tip: Check Cobblemon Farmers for special farm layouts that boost berry yields.&r"
