		}
		{
			description: [
				"Certain Cobblemon have field abilities that interact with crops and plants around them. Grass and Water types are the most common — place them near your farm and watch what happens."
				""
				"This is the Cobblemon Farmers integration at work: your Cobblemon aren't just fighters, they're workers. A Cobblemon with the right field ability can accelerate crop growth, water soil, or even protect your farm from pests."
				""
				"Experiment with different types near different crops. Not every ability works on every plant."
				""
				"&7Tip: Grass and Water types often have field abilities — try them near crops.&r"
			]
