		{
			dependencies: ["1000000000000085"]
			description: [
				"Hostile mobs trample crops and undo your farming work in seconds. A Cobblemon stationed near your farm in defend mode will intercept and fight off anything that gets too close."
				""
				"Set an aggressive Cobblemon to 'defend area' mode and position it near your berry rows. Let it handle the hostile mobs while you focus on harvesting and planting."
				""
				"This is Cobblemon filling a role that horses and iron golems used to. Your partner is more capable — let it prove that."
				""
				"&7Tip: Set a Cobblemon to 'defend area' mode to ward off hostile mobs automatically.&r"
